                "invention-title": [
                    "System and method for preparing synthesis gas with adjustable hydrogen-carbon ratio from biomass",
                    "一种生物质制备氢碳比可调合成气的系统和方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a system and method for preparing synthesis gas with an adjustable hydrogen-carbon ratio from biomass, and relates to the technical field of energy utilization, the system at least comprises a gasification furnace, a gas-liquid separation unit, a tar clarifying tank, a CO-rich synthesis gas purification unit, an electrolysis unit, an H2 purification unit and a CO2 separation and storage unit, the gasification furnace is respectively connected with the gas-liquid separation unit and the CO2 separation and storage unit through pipelines, the gas-liquid separation unit is respectively connected with the tar clarifying tank, the CO-rich synthesis gas purification unit and the electrolysis unit through pipelines, and the electrolysis unit is connected with the H2 purification unit through a pipeline. According to the method, CO generation, H2 generation and combustion heat supply reaction in the gasification process are decoupled, so that the hydrogen-carbon ratio of the synthesis gas is flexibly adjusted according to the requirements of downstream chemicals, CO2 generation in the biomass gasification process is reduced, and the purpose of efficiently and flexibly preparing the synthesis gas with the adjustable hydrogen-carbon ratio from the biomass is achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种生物质制备氢碳比可调合成气的系统和方法，涉及能源利用技术领域，至少包括气化炉、气液分离单元、焦油澄清槽、富CO合成气净化单元、电解单元、H2净化单元和CO2分离储存单元，所述气化炉分别与气液分离单元和CO2分离储存单元通过管道相连，所述气液分离单元分别与焦油澄清槽、富CO合成气净化单元和电解单元通过管道相连，所述电解单元与H2净化单元通过管道相连。本发明通过解耦气化过程中CO生成、H2生成和燃烧供热反应，实现了合成气氢碳比根据下游化学品的需求灵活调整，降低了生物质气化过程中CO2的生成，从而实现了生物质高效灵活制备氢碳比可调合成气的目标。"
                }
            ]
